Prediction section: Correlation between lm 1, 2, 3 shows my model a has a perfect correlation

pred1 <- predict(lm1, newdata = test)
pred2 <- predict(lm2, newdata = test)
pred3 <- predict(lm3, newdata = test)
cor1 <- cor(pred1, test$capital.loss)
print(paste('correlaton: ', cor1))

cor2 <- cor(pred2, test$capital.loss)
